### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@noteId = replace_with_note_id

### Create a new note
POST {{baseUrl}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Note",
  "content": "This is the content of my first note",
  "tags": ["personal", "thoughts"]
}

### Get all notes
GET {{baseUrl}}/notes

### Update a note
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notes/{{noteId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Note Title",
  "content": "This is the updated content",
  "tags": ["personal", "updated"]
}

### Example with real data - Create a Todo note
POST {{baseUrl}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Shopping List",
  "content": "1. Milk\n2. Bread\n3. Eggs",
  "tags": ["shopping", "todo"]
}

### Example with real data - Create a Meeting note
POST {{baseUrl}}/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Team Meeting Notes",
  "content": "- Discussed project timeline\n- Assigned tasks\n- Next meeting on Friday",
  "tags": ["work", "meetings"]
